 "en|Rule window. Well done! Rule 4: Petit Bridge is a team game, play without wasting! Watch the cards your partner plays. If your partner is going to win the trick, do not play your strongest card: keep it to win another trick later. Press 1 to close and continue": "b4ecaff41d762025.mp3",
